		$specification """
			[Test Goal]
				Verify that IcuHdl_TimerNoti_LowPulseMeasure correctly takes the FALSE branch: ICUHDL_PULSE_MAX == lowPulse_u16 (PULSE_MAX != lowPulse FALSE arm), highPulse == 0 (highPulse != 0 FALSE arm)
			[Precondition]
