				Execute IcuHdl_TimerNoti_LowPulseMeasure() targeting: ICUHDL_PULSE_MAX == lowPulse_u16 (PULSE_MAX != lowPulse FALSE arm), highPulse == 0 (highPulse != 0 FALSE arm). Expected outcome: `ICUHDL_PULSE_MAX != IcuHdl_PulseDataBak_st[].lowPulse_u16` FALSE branch.
